{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Emerald Geography is a quiz game that helps you learn the countries and capitals of the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiple Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Find</strong>:<strong> </strong>In this mode, you'll see the name of a country or capital and must click it on the globe. If you're wrong three times, you'll be taken to the correct location.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Type</strong>: In this mode, you'll be taken to a country or capital and must type its name. If you make a mistake, you'll get a hint.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Explore</strong>: Freely explore the world. You'll see the names of countries and capitals as you hover over them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Learn by Region</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Africa </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Americas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Asia </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Europe </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Oceania</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Randomized Quiz  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once you are comfortable with the entire world, use the randomized modes to keep things interesting. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Random 10 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Random 50 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Score </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn more points for quickly getting correct answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiple Themes </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Change the look of the globe and learn in style.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3171440?t=1739937146","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171440/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739937146","capsule_image":"htt